#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><u>Add Resources</u></b>: Easily add resources like classes or coaches to "
"your system."
msgstr ""
"<b><u>Dodaj vire</u></b>: V svoj sistem preprosto dodajte vire, kot so "
"tečaji ali trenerji."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><u>Comprehensive Scheduling</u></b>: Plan and manage schedules, allowing "
"customers to book appointments directly from your website, manage classes "
"and sessions, and track attendance."
msgstr ""
"<b><u>Celovito razporejanje</u></b>: Načrtujte in upravljajte urnike, kar "
"strankam omogoča rezervacijo terminov neposredno z vašega spletnega mesta, "
"upravljanje tečajev in sej ter spremljanje udeležbe."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><u>Customize Availability</u></b>: Set availability for different "
"resources, ensuring that your scheduling system is always up-to-date."
msgstr ""
"<b><u>Prilagodi razpoložljivost</u></b>: Nastavite razpoložljivost za "
"različne vire in tako zagotovite, da je vaš sistem za razporejanje vedno "
"posodobljen."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><u>Link to Courses</u></b>: Connect resources to specific courses that "
"can be either free or paid, depending on the user’s subscription status."
msgstr ""
"<b><u>Povezava do tečajev</u></b>: Povežite vire z določenimi tečaji, ki so "
"lahko brezplačni ali plačljivi, odvisno od stanja naročnine uporabnika."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<b><u>Website Integration</u></b>: Seamlessly integrate all these features "
"into your website, providing a unified experience for your customers to book "
"appointments, view class schedules, and manage subscriptions online."
msgstr ""
"<b><u>Integracija spletnih strani</u></b>: Vse te funkcije brezhibno "
"integrirajte v svoje spletno mesto in tako svojim strankam zagotovite enotno "
"izkušnjo za rezervacijo terminov, ogled urnikov predavanj in upravljanje "
"naročnin prek spleta."

