#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.aboutus
msgid ""
"Aline is one of the iconic people in life who can say they love what they "
"do. She mentors 100+ in-house trainers and looks after the community of "
"fitness enthusiasts."
msgstr ""
"Andreja je ena izmed ikoničnih osebnosti, ki lahko reče, da ljubi to, kar "
"počne. Je mentorica več kot 100 internim trenerjem in skrbi za skupnost "
"ljubiteljev fitnesa."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid "Appointment, classes &amp; courses"
msgstr "Termin, predavanja &amp; tečaji"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As the first invoicing step, create a down payment from the sales order. "
"This will generate the first invoice in the\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Invoicing</font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            app. Then, schedule one or several \"Invoicing Schedule\" "
"activities on the sales order with the aim to never forget to send an "
"intermediary invoice in order to sustain your cash flow"
msgstr ""
"Kot prvi korak pri izstavljanju računov ustvarite predplačilo iz prodajnega "
"naročila. To bo ustvarilo prvi račun v aplikaciji\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Izdajanje računov</font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            Nato v prodajnem naročilu načrtujte eno ali več dejavnosti "
"»Razporeda izstavljanja računov«, da nikoli ne pozabite poslati vmesnega "
"računa, da ohranite svoj denarni tok."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time, create customized subscriptions for your members that clearly "
"display pricing, discounts, and details of each:"
msgstr ""
"Kadar koli lahko za svoje člane ustvarite prilagojene naročnine, ki jasno "
"prikazujejo cene, popuste in podrobnosti o vsakem od:"

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.homepage
msgid ""
"At our fitness center, we believe that fitness is not just about working "
"out. It's about creating a lifestyle that promotes health and wellness. Let "
"us help you achieve your fitness goals and live your best life."
msgstr ""
"V našem fitnes centru verjamemo, da fitnes ni samo vadba. Gre za ustvarjanje "
"življenjskega sloga, ki spodbuja zdravje in dobro počutje. Naj vam pomagamo "
"doseči vaše fitnes cilje in živeti najboljše življenje."

#. module: fitness
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:fitness.aboutus
msgid ""
"At our gym club, we offer a diverse range of classes and programs tailored "
"to meet your fitness needs. Whether you are a beginner looking to start your "
"fitness journey or a seasoned athlete aiming to enhance your performance, we "
"have something for everyone. Our classes include yoga, personal training "
"sessions, and various group fitness activities designed to keep you "
"motivated and engaged. Join us to experience a supportive community and "
"achieve your fitness goals in a fun and effective way."
msgstr ""
"V našem telovadnem klubu ponujamo raznoliko paleto tečajev in programov, "
"prilagojenih vašim fitnes potrebam. Ne glede na to, ali ste začetnik, ki "
"želi začeti svojo fitnes pot, ali izkušen športnik, ki želi izboljšati svojo "
"zmogljivost, imamo nekaj za vsakogar. Naši tečaji vključujejo jogo, osebne "
"treninge in različne skupinske fitnes aktivnosti, zasnovane tako, da vas "
"motivirajo in angažirajo. Pridružite se nam, da izkusite podporno skupnost "
"in dosežete svoje fitnes cilje na zabaven in učinkovit način."

